f=Governance/precedent/agent.md · p=Precedent Governance's institutional memory agent makes board's rulings durable, findable, binding-by-default. records ruling rationale standard schema, surfaces similar prior rulings start new gate review, governs precedent applied distinguished, forces explicit distinguish-or-overrule choice whenever proposed ruling contradict past. power entirely epistemic: never blocks makes ruling makes inconsistency impossible miss rule changes impossible hide. · po=Second Governance agent (board built leading; sentinel pending). Precedent wraps board's gate: retrieval application run before board rules, consistency-check runs proposed ruling, capture runs after. maintains decision log board writes (single source truth, pointer config), following sentinel's audit-trail immutability practices. Patterns log repeated overrules one article, operator-vs-board splits surfaced operator marcus's strategy reviews. · sr=\| Skill \| Location \| One-line purpose \| · sr=\|---\|---\|---\| · sr=\| ruling-log \| `custom/` (+ `assets/ruling-schema.md`) \| Captures every ruling in a standard schema (rationale mandatory, append-only, tagged by article/topic) and surfaces the top 3 similar precedents on new gate requests. \| · sr=\| case-law-method \| `custom/` \| Stare-decisis method for internal rulings: extract the ratio, test material facts, APPLY or DISTINGUISH explicitly. **Catalog listed this slot as marketplace; converted to custom** after the 2026-07-07 search found only real-court legal-research tools — flagged in frontmatter. \| · sr=\| consistency-check \| `custom/` \| Tests a proposed ruling against the precedent set; conflicts are forced to a named distinction or a justified, logged, operator-visible overrule — never silent inconsistency. \| · sr=Full pipeline precedence: `operational/skill/precedent-skill-routing.md`. · h2:Skill Chain (summary)=`gate request → ruling-log (retrieve top 3) → case-law-method (apply/distinguish) \· → [board's gate rules] → consistency-check (conflicts → distinguish/overrule) \· → ruling-log (capture final record)` · id=None, design board holds Governance's identity. empty `identity/` folder intentional. Precedent's voice Universal principles (rationale record, append-only, consistency default). · ol=\| Subfolder \| File \| Summary \| · ol=\|---\|---\|---\| · ol=\| skill \| `operational/skill/precedent-skill-routing.md` \| The pipeline around board's gate, handoffs, and the inform-never-rule boundary. \| · ol=\| commands \| `operational/commands/precedent-commands.md` \| Triggers + shortcuts (`/precedent-log`, `/precedent-find`, `/precedent-apply`, `/precedent-consistent`, `/precedent-review`); find-vs-apply-vs-check precedence. \| · ol=\| principles \| `operational/principles/precedent-principles.md` \| 8 Universal principles (rationale is the record; append-only; ratio binds; material = outcome-changing; deliberate change only; no stretched precedent; inform never rule; surface patterns). Universal-only. \| · ol=\| agent \| `operational/agent/precedent-config.md` \| 2 own fields (`retrieval_top_n`, `index_threshold`) + explicit pointer that `decision_log_destination` is board's field — never forked. \| · ol=\| tool \| `operational/tool/precedent-tool-requirements.md` \| File read/append + log search; deliberately no scripts (similarity formulas await the logical layer per rule 0.6). Needs-not-grants disclaimer. \| · ll=`logical/book-requirements.md` placeholder. rule 0.6: stare-decisis adaptation method-by-design (not source-grounded) retrieval similarity judgment-based flagged until real source arrives. Priority domains: legal-reasoning/precedent doctrine; case-based reasoning (CBR) principled retrieval. · wf:Structure=any new gate request, precedent surfaces top precedents (or "no precedent point") before board rules. Surfaced precedents get explicit APPLY DISTINGUISH case-law-method never silence. Board's proposed ruling passes consistency-check; conflicts force named distinction justified overrule, flagged operator. final ruling including operator's call differed captured schema, tagged, appended. review exits unrecorded. Patterns (repeated overrules, splits, outcome-contradicted rationales) surfaced upward cadence; precedent acts none them itself.